64
00:05:02,150 --> 00:05:04,030
C-Consigo!

65
00:05:07,910 --> 00:05:10,280
Yuuki, consegue ler?

66
00:05:10,280 --> 00:05:11,450
Claro.

67
00:05:11,450 --> 00:05:13,700
Eu estudei bastante sozinha.

68
